org.openscience.cdk.smsd.algorithm.mcgregor

Class McGregor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openscience.cdk.smsd.algorithm.mcgregor.McGregor

  • @TestClass(value="org.openscience.cdk.smsd.algorithm.mcgregor.McGregorTest")
public final class McGregor
extends Object
    Class which reports MCS solutions based on the McGregor algorithm published in 1982.

    The SMSD algorithm is described in this paper. please refer Rahman et.al. 2009 [Rahman, S.A. and Bashton, M. and Holliday, G.L. and Schrader, R. and Thornton, J.M. , Small Molecule Subgraph Detector (SMSD) Toolkit, Journal of Cheminformatics, 2009, 1:12].

    Author:
    Syed Asad Rahman
    Belongs to CDK module:
    smsd
    Source code:
    master
